               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Bromfed<sup>®</sup> DM Cough Syrup is a clear, light pink syrup with a butterscotch flavor.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Each 5 mL (1 teaspoonful) contains:</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Brompheniramine Maleate, USP     . . . . . . . .  2 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Pseudoephedrine Hydrochloride, USP . . . . . 30 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Dextromethorphan Hydrobromide, USP  . . . 10 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Alcohol 0.95% v/v</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>In a palatable, aromatic vehicle.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Inactive Ingredients: artificial butterscotch flavor, citric acid anhydrous, dehydrated alcohol, FD&amp;C Red No. 40, glycerin, liquid sugar, methylparaben, propylene glycol, purified water and sodium benzoate. It may contain 10% citric acid solution or 10% sodium citrate solution for pH adjustment. The pH range is between 3.0 and 6.0.</paragraph>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1">
                     <caption>C<sub>16</sub>H<sub>19</sub>BrN<sub>2</sub>•C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>4</sub>O<sub>4</sub>          M.W. 435.31 							</caption>
                  </renderMultiMedia>
                  <table width="100%" ID="ib9a981c0-feba-4d4f-8e1d-7d1fb6fc09d8">
                     <col width="100%" align="center" valign="middle"/>
